        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "ConvertStringDateToDate",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " function is a scalar function in Microsoft SQL Server designed to convert a date represented as a string into a SQL Server "
