          "type": "text",
          "text": "DATE",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " data type. This function is useful when dealing with data imported from external sources where dates are stored as strings, and there is a need to perform date operations or comparisons."
